name: ImpactXP
description: Give rise to communities across the globe. Even though at the center is the Impactor, we believe that with the power of community and the coming together of various individuals to form communities, we can overcome the various obstacles we face. With the IMPACTXP platform, the token and its ecosystem, our mission is to spark the birth of such communities and make an impact in the realm of Finance, Ecology, Art and all things concerning crypto. We will keep inspiring future Impactors.
